title: Presidential Nomination Sent to the Senate, 6/10/10 | whitehouse.gov
content:
The White House
Office of the Press Secretary


For Immediate Release
June 10, 2010

 



Presidential Nomination Sent to the Senate, 6/10/10




James E. Graves, Jr., of Mississippi, to be United States Circuit Judge for the Fifth Circuit, vice Rhesa H. Barksdale, retired.
